<p id="fs-idm36976592">(a) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>14</mn></mrow><mn>34</mn></msubsup><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>14</mn></mrow><mn>34</mn></msubsup><mtext>X</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p><p id="fs-idp91657136">(b) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.3em"/><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><mn>36</mn></msubsup><mtext>P</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.3em"/><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><mn>36</mn></msubsup><mtext>P</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p><p id="fs-idm47972736">(c) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.3em"/><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><mn>57</mn></msubsup><mtext>Mn</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.3em"/><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><mn>57</mn></msubsup><mtext>Mn</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p><p id="fs-idm2927904">(d) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.5em"/><mn>56</mn></mrow><mn>121</mn></msubsup><mtext>X</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.5em"/><mn>56</mn></mrow><mn>121</mn></msubsup><mtext>X</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p></div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp81897760">
<p id="fs-idm87925664">(a) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>14</mn></mrow><mn>34</mn></msubsup><mtext>Si</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>14</mn></mrow><mn>34</mn></msubsup><mtext>Si</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> (b) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><mn>36</mn></msubsup><mtext>P</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><mn>36</mn></msubsup><mtext>P</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> (c) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>25</mn></mrow><mn>57</mn></msubsup><mtext>Mn</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mn>25</mn></mrow><mn>57</mn></msubsup><mtext>Mn</mtext><mo>;</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> (d) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.5em"/><mn>56</mn></mrow><mn>121</mn></msubsup><mtext>Ba</mtext></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><msubsup><mrow/><mrow><mspace width="0.5em"/><mn>56</mn></mrow><mn>121</mn></msubsup><mtext>Ba</mtext></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p></div>
